Text: C'mon guys!!!!  Write some COMMENTS!  When you download - the LEAST you can do is write something about the quality of video + sound. I don't care if it does say BlueRay - I've gotten some BlueRay videos here that look worse than a camcorder shot in a theater with a 5-year-old print!  So let us know what you think. If it's good - for god sakes, THANK THE MAN (OR WOMAN)!
so, how good is the quality?
